
Aim: Design Christmas dual led chaser lights.
Apparatus: Arduino, LEDâ€™s, Resistance 470 ohm, 
wires,Breadboard 

Program -

void setup()
{

for (int i = 10; i <= 13; i++) 
{
 pinMode(i, OUTPUT);
 } 
} 
void loop(){
 for (int i = 10; i <14; i++) 
{
 allLEDsOff();
if (i!=13){
 digitalWrite(i,HIGH);
 digitalWrite(i+1,HIGH);
 delay(200);
 } 
 else
 digitalWrite(i,HIGH);
 digitalWrite(i-3,HIGH);
 delay(200);
 allLEDsOff();
 } 
} 
void allLEDsOff(void)
{ 
 for (int i = 10; i <= 14; i++) 
{
 digitalWrite(i, LOW);
 
 } 
 delay(100);
} 
Result
Chasing of LED was verified after uploading the program. 
